if exists (select 1

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: PROPERTY */
/*==============================================================*/
create table PROPERTY (
PROPERTY varchar(20) not null,
PROPERTY_PARENT varchar(20) null,
CATEGORY varchar(50) null,
SQLTYPE varchar(20) null
constraint CKC_SQLTYPE_PROPERTY check (SQLTYPE is null or (SQLTYPE in ('VARCHAR','LONGVARCHAR','NUMERIC','DECIMAL','BIT','TINYINT','SMALLINT','INTEGER','BIGINT','REAL','FLOAT','DOUBLE','BINARY','VARBINARY','LONGVARBINARY','DATE','TIME','TIMESTAMP'))),
TYPE varchar(20) null default 'DIRECT'
constraint CKC_TYPE_PROPERTY check (TYPE is null or (TYPE in ('DIRECT','SQLVALUE','SYSTEM'))),
DATASOURCE varchar(20) null,
IS_MULTIVALUE varchar(10) null default 'NO'
constraint CKC_IS_MULTIVALUE_PROPERTY check (IS_MULTIVALUE is null or (IS_MULTIVALUE in ('YES','NO'))),
VALUE varchar(1000) null,
constraint PK_PROPERTY primary key nonclustered (PROPERTY)
)
go

Column TYPE of the table PROPERTY

Card of the column TYPE of the table PROPERTY

Name

TYPE

Code

TYPE

Data Type

varchar(20)

Mandatory

No


Description of the column TYPE of the table PROPERTY

DIRECT .- Valor directo
Se toma el dato definido de la columna VALUE
Se tratara como el tipo de valor definido en SQLTYPE

SQL_VALUE
Se considera en la columna VALUE la consulta SQL que regresara el valor a considerar como valor del parametro,
Importante: la consulta solo debe de regresar una columna con con una ó varias filas
Ejemplo: "Select getdate()"
